Data Normalization

Since market information may come from different providers, all responses should be normalized into a consistent internal format.

Example:

{
  "asset": "ETH",
  "price": 3348.42,
  "currency": "USD",
  "volume_24h": 14800000000,
  "volatility": 4.2,
  "source": "Chainlink"
}
